          </choice>grāhārake bhujyamānaka-kṣetrapada<surplus>ṁ</surplus>m a<lb break="no" n="4"/>
nyac ca lohakārapallikāyā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> pūrvva-bhujyamānakam eva kṣetraṁ brahmadeya-krameṇa<surplus>ṁ</surplus>
<lb n="5"/><choice>
